    "weekly_narrative": "本週全球市場陷入中東衝突與粘性通膨的雙重夾擊。隨着 WTI 原油站上 89.6 美元，生產端成本壓力顯著增強，導致 PPI 數據創下三年新高，市場基本排除了本月降息的可能性。US10Y 殖利率維持在 4.309% 的高位，反映出債市正與通膨預期進行劇烈拉鋸。值得注意的是，儘管美元指數 DXY 位於 98.227，但資金正加速逃向實體資產與數位黃金，推升黃金至 4814.4 美元及比特幣至 74776.09 美元，顯示投資者在法幣系統外尋求避險。",
    "next_week_forecast_html": "<details class='analysis-container'><summary>📢 下週預測：能源通膨與債市拉鋸戰</summary><div class='analysis-content'><strong>⛓️ 市場邏輯傳導：</strong><p>伊朗衝突持續 ➔ 影響<strong>能源供應與 PPI 成本</strong> ➔ 推升<strong>美債殖利率並壓抑降息預期</strong> ➔ 最終定價<strong>美元高位震盪與避險資產走強</strong>。</p><hr><strong>📉 資產動態預測：</strong><ul><li><strong>亞洲貨幣 (TWD/JPY/KRW)：</strong>隨原油報價維持高位，輸入型通膨壓力將迫使亞幣維持防禦性弱勢。</li><li><strong>避險成本與鋼鐵業：</strong>黃金與比特幣的高漲顯示市場對信用貨幣的不信任，傳統製造業將面臨融資成本與原材料雙重成本上升。</li></ul></div></details>",
    "focus_html": "\n        <div class=\"focus-card\">\n            <div class=\"focus-idx\">01</div>\n            <div class=\"focus-content\">\n                <h4>中東衝突與通膨螺旋</h4>\n                <p>伊朗衝突引發市場對供應鏈的二次恐懼，招聘凍結與薪資壓力共存，聯準會決策陷入兩難。</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"focus-card\">\n            <div class=\"focus-idx\">02</div>\n            <div class=\"focus-content\">\n                <h4>AI 能源需求與生產力轉型</h4>\n                <p>AI 技術對能源的龐大需求與對就業市場的潛在衝擊（20% 失業風險）成為結構性通膨的新動能。</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
    "fx_rates_linkage": "當前 US10Y 報 4.309%，美債高殖利率本應支撐美元強勢，但 DXY 僅微幅升至 98.227。這反映出非美央行因輸入型通膨壓力被迫轉鷹，利差優勢遭稀釋。同時，原油報價 89.6 美元加劇了亞幣貶值壓力，資金正繞過傳統匯市流入黃金與比特幣避險。",
    "tbody_html": "\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">🔥 通膨預期</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">CPI/PPI Outlook</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-up\">持續擴張 <span class=\"status_detail\">PPI 創三年新高，原油報價 89.6 美元推升生產端成本。</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-up \">上升螺旋</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">地緣政治、AI 能源需求、供應鏈成本回升。</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">📉 利率預期</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">Fed Funds / US10Y</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-up\">高位橫盤 <span class=\"status_detail\">US10Y 報 4.309%，市場已排除本月降息可能性。</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-up \">偏鷹盤整</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">粘性通膨數據、就業市場強韌、油價上揚。</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">🦅 美元指數</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">DXY Strength</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-up\">擴張受阻 <span class=\"status_detail\">DXY 報 98.227，利差優勢被非美央行鷹派態度稀釋。</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-up \">橫盤偏弱</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">避險資產分流至黃金與比特幣、非美央行轉鷹。</td>\n                </tr>",
    "risk_html": "\n        <div class=\"risk-item\">\n            <span class=\"risk-title\">⚠️ 滯脹風險升溫</span>\n            <p class=\"risk-content\">若油價持續受地緣政治推動超過 90 美元，高利率與高通膨並存將重創企業資本支出。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"risk-item\">\n            <span class=\"risk-title\">⚠️ 債券市場崩潰壓力</span>\n            <p class=\"risk-content\">十年期公債殖利率若進一步突破前高，將觸發科技股估值修正與金融體系流動性緊縮。</p>\n        </div>",
    "news_html": "\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMinwFBVV95cUxQdi1HWnNmZ2JtQmM5VjBtZFR0MUZDdHh5djhoUnZORS0yOTdGb01ocHhScU5USWdpSGs2bzhBXzlkS0FHYVRoUkM3b0VuWENwZ1lSeUkteVBWaXJiYW9xdXVWUG5jck1ja3hlSkVORUxZcndKUTBlbW5aTTBCVUZWS0VXaDhRclVVNjBGMHJNMlpJMEk2cVRNTEVaM3VtQzQ?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Economic Impact of Iran Conflict: Hiring Freezes, Inflation, and Fed Uncertainty - News and Statistics - IndexBox</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiZkFVX3lxTE1PcmdpYzdnSTBWckxQM0FmcmxiNUYzWW9Va2hlQ3B0d0R2THp1ZXpMMU9yeTlCak5OY3V6aHhycUE4NVlHZEVqUDB6eGIzcXJjNC1La1VwT3YzVjFmODVxRXJ3V05NZw?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Inflation, deflation, and the “Goldilocks scenario” - Britannica</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMisgFBVV95cUxQaGs5U1FBaVdzb2NKQ1M2ZXVrMUNYUlNIRTF0VXRmS1RRUlRYZ1lPNFBMUEVOWmhnM0h5UmZSOEZLYW9YcjhhTV9Wb2t3amlGdmV6dThuM1hRbFVZVzN6d1ZrWU9DNkJfSVd1ek9HcGoxQ2x5eHk0dE1vZDJoZUFZbDRiNU1fUHh2UnhoSkh6YVBJNS1JYTJnSnp3VTNVS1FTLU03R1ZQOG1KTUJfR2d2aWlR?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Inflation or recession? The tug of war in bond markets - The Economist</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Is AI going to lead to 20% unemployment - or just make your employees superhuman? - Insurance Business</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 10-year Treasury yield hovers near 4.3% after oil price gain, sticky inflation data - CNBC</a>\n                </li>",
