  {
    "date": "2026-04-15 23:04",
    "weekly_narrative": "本週全球金融市場陷入「結構性通膨」與「地緣政治僵局」的雙重夾擊。隨著 3 月批發物價指數 (PPI) 創下三年新高，市場對聯準會短期內降息的期待幾近破滅，特別是在伊朗談判破裂後，能源價格對通膨的傳導效應愈發顯著。美國十年期公債殖利率 (US10Y) 穩守 4.275% 高位，反映出市場正重新定價長期高利率 (Higher for Longer) 的現實。然而，美元指數 (DXY) 報 98.114 表現相對壓抑，主因在於資金流向黃金與加密貨幣等抗通膨資產，黃金價格衝上 4836.8 美元，顯示投資者正積極尋求法定貨幣體系外的避險出口。",
    "next_week_forecast_html": "<details class='analysis-container'><summary>📢 下週預測：粘性通膨下的資產重組</summary><div class='analysis-content'><strong>⛓️ 市場邏輯傳導：</strong><p>地緣政治緊張導致能源價格居高不下 ➔ 強化 <strong>PPI/CPI 粘性</strong> ➔ 迫使聯準會維持 <strong>高利率立場</strong> ➔ 資金在<strong>高收益美債</strong>與<strong>抗通膨實體資產</strong>（黃金/BTC）之間重新配置。</p><hr><strong>📉 資產動態預測：</strong><ul><li><strong>亞洲貨幣 (TWD/JPY/KRW)：</strong>儘管美元指數目前報 98.114 未再突破，但因原油成本高企，亞幣仍將面臨進口通膨帶來的貿易帳壓力。</li><li><strong>避險成本與鋼鐵業：</strong>黃金報價來到 4836.8 美元反映極端避險情緒，鋼鐵與能源密集型產業將因 PPI 持續上升而面臨利潤擠壓。</li></ul></div></details>",
    "focus_html": "\n        <div class=\"focus-card\">\n            <div class=\"focus-idx\">01</div>\n            <div class=\"focus-content\">\n                <h4>通膨二次噴發：PPI 創三年新高</h4>\n                <p>最新數據顯示批發端通膨壓力未減，PPI 的超預期增長強化了能源與 AI 算力需求帶來的成本推動型通膨。這使得九成以上的美國年長勞工因通膨壓力被迫調整退休計劃，經濟基本面呈現強勁但伴隨高生活成本的特徵。</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"focus-card\">\n            <div class=\"focus-idx\">02</div>\n            <div class=\"focus-content\">\n                <h4>中東局勢惡化：伊朗談判破裂</h4>\n                <p>地緣政治風險是本週最重要的驅動因子。伊朗談判無果而終，直接導致原油價格支撐在 92.3 美元，不僅推升了通膨預期，更封鎖了聯準會本月採取任何寬鬆行動的可能性，債券市場拋售壓力隨之增加。</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
    "fx_rates_linkage": "當前利率與匯率的傳導邏輯出現分化。儘管美國 10 年期公債殖利率維持在 4.275% 的高位，理論上應支撐強勢美元，但由於全球央行（如韓國央行）紛紛轉向鷹派以對抗進口通膨，加上黃金價格飆漲至 4836.8 美元奪走部分避險資金，導致美元指數 (DXY) 僅維持在 98.114 盤整。這種『高殖利率、偏軟美元』的現象，揭示了市場對單一貨幣購買力的疑慮，資金轉向實體與去中心化資產的趨勢明顯。",
    "tbody_html": "\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">🔥 通膨預期</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">CPI/PPI Outlook</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-up\">持續擴張 <span class=\"status_detail\">PPI 創下三年新高，原油維持在 92.3 美元，能源成本持續向終端傳導。</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-up \">上升螺旋</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">地緣政治緊張、AI 能源需求、工資增長滯後。</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">📉 利率預期</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">Fed Funds / US10Y</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-up\">高位橫盤 <span class=\"status_detail\">US10Y 報 4.275%，市場已完全抹除本月降息的可能性。</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-up \">偏鷹盤整</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">伊朗談判破裂、粘性通膨數據、就業市場穩健。</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">🦅 美元指數</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">DXY Strength</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-up\">擴張受阻 <span class=\"status_detail\">DXY 報 98.114，雖有高利差支撐但受非美貨幣抗通膨政策抵消。</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-up \">橫盤偏弱</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">避險資產分流（BTC/Gold）、非美央行鷹派抬頭。</td>\n                </tr>",
    "risk_html": "\n        <div class=\"risk-item\">\n            <span class=\"risk-title\">⚠️ AI 帶來的結構性失業與電力通膨</span>\n            <p class=\"risk-content\">市場正擔憂 AI 普及可能引發高達 20% 的失業率，同時 AI 數據中心對電力的高需求將長期支撐能源價格，形成通膨與衰退並存的潛在風險。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"risk-item\">\n            <span class=\"risk-title\">⚠️ 全球央行跟進鷹派立場</span>\n            <p class=\"risk-content\">加拿大與韓國央行已展現強硬抗通膨決心。若全球進入加息競賽，將對標普 500 目前 6991.44 的高估值水平構成估值修正壓力。</p>\n        </div>",
    "news_html": "\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Is AI going to lead to 20% unemployment - or just make your employees superhuman? - Insurance Business</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Wholesale inflation rose in March to three year-high - WPSD Local 6</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMisgFBVV95cUxQaGs5U1FBaVdzb2NKQ1M2ZXVrMUNYUlNIRTF0VXRmS1RRUlRYZ1lPNFBMUEVOWmhnM0h5UmZSOEZLYW9YcjhhTV9Wb2t3amlGdmV6dThuM1hRbFVZVzN6d1ZrWU9DNkJfSVd1ek9HcGoxQ2x5eHk0dE1vZDJoZUFZbDRiNU1fUHh2UnhoSkh6YVBJNS1JYTJnSnp3VTNVS1FTLU03R1ZQOG1KTUJfR2d2aWlR?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Inflation or recession? The tug of war in bond markets - The Economist</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 10-year Treasury yield hovers near 4.3% after oil price gain, sticky inflation data - CNBC</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Nine in ten older US workers say inflation is reshaping their retirement plans - InvestmentNews</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMihgFBVV95cUxNRVVXQmhEMW51SjNTVDdNeUdTWDJQVVpjZGozRHgyRFlFSEhGVFAydzZyQ3Bya3cxUFN5Y01MUUJmeEdhYkRUYUp1UXRqbWFiS1dNMjEyaEJZNlFOTVk0anh4ZkpMbGhncGxKa2RsNl9BZG9zcFR5SHRBcENOZWY3Y3ZESVBZUQ?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Investors are writing off any move from the Fed this month. Collapsing talks in Iran have sealed the deal - Fortune</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://new